text: Ieronymos II (, ; born 30 March 1938) is the Archbishop of Athens and All Greece. He is the primate of the Autocephalous Orthodox Church of Greece. He was elected on 7 February 2008." Greek Orthodox bishops elect leader" , CNN.com/europe.
